headline: Wells Fargo Updates 2026 Earnings Release Date Information
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, February 20, 2026--Wells Fargo & Company (NYSE: WFC) today updated its expected earnings release dates and conference call information for 2026. For each of the earnings dates below, financial results will be released at approximately 7:00 a.m. Eastern time, and the live conference call will be at 10:00 a.m. Eastern time. Confirmation of these calls, as well as details on how to listen, will be provided before the scheduled release dates.
